  output.concat '   0.12.2 - fix(gemcutter): Checks song status once when a Purify batch starts, saves the current renewal cost as mana to preserve, treats no active songs as no renewal reserve, waits before casting when mana is too close to song renewal, lets Gemcutter setup save separate patterns for regular gems, purified non-orbs, pure orbs, and chrisms, keeps Analyze Box from crashing after saving designs, and makes Analyze Box capture output without a slow manual get loop.' + "\n"
  output.concat "\n"
