  output.concat '   0.11.0 - feat(gemcutter): Kept real bag names when saved scan rows say worn/held, made Purify updates immediately refresh matching Review rows with orb, chrism, purified, and moved-bag status, uses saved orb, chrism, and purified bag settings to recognize saved gem states when item IDs change, keeps exact item-ID status above bag hints, uses the least-specific shared status when saved bags overlap, made Review/Sell and Ignore container checks explain themselves, stay exclusive, and hide ignored containers from the Review/Sell list, keeps the source bag from the scan when building Review rows, added a Gemcutter setup tab that saves cutter, pattern, and lapidary box details, analyzes lapidary boxes for unlocked designs, and stops Purify safely after low mana, system shock, or overextension before grabbing another gem.' + "\n"
